			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Siampi liante le Thukham hilh siate in hong neh uh a, Jesuh mawhsakna thu nakpitakin hong gen uh hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Tua ciangin Herod le galkapte in Jesuh zahko-in simmawh bawl uh a, kumpi puantualpi a silhsak khit uh ciangin Pilat kiangah a puakkik uh hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hih hun ma-in Herod le Pilat kilem loin kigalbawl uh a, ahi zongin tua ni mahmahin amau tegel kilem kikin kipawlbawl uh hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Pilat in zong siampi liante, upate, le mihonpite sam khawmin",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> amaute kiangah, “Hih mipa in i mipihte lam khialsak hi, ci-in mawhsakin kei kiangah nong paipih uh hi. Note khempeuh mai mahah amah thu ka sit a, amah na mawhsakna uh thute khat beekah a mawhna ka mu kei hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tua mah bangin Herod in zong ama mawhna mu lo a, eite kiangah amah hong puakkik hi. Hih mipa in sihna a thuak nadingin ama gamtatna bangmah om lo hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Tua ahih manin amah satna tawh thuhilhin ka khah ding hi,” a ci hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> (Paisan Pawi hun simin Pilat in amaute’ deih thongkia khat a khah ding ahi hi.)",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Tua ciangin mihon khempeuh kiko uh a, “Amah that in! Barabbas hong khahsak in!” a ci uh hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Barabbas pen khua sungah mi a buaisakna hang, le mi a thahna hangin thong sungah a kikhum ahi hi.",
