			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ahi zongin a aw neihzah uh tawh amaute awng semsem uh a, singlamteh tungah Jesuh a thah nading gen uh ahih manin a tawpna-ah a zo uh hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Tua ahih manin amaute’ ngetna bangin piak dingin Pilat in thu a khen hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Mi buaisakna le mi thahna hangin thong sungah a kikhia mipa amau’ ngetna bangin khah a, amau’ deihna bangin a bawl dingun Jesuh a piakhia hi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Tua ciangin amaute in Jesuh paikhiatpih uh a, gam sung panin khuapi sungah a hong pai, Sairin khuami Simon a kici mi khat tawh a kituak uh hi. Amaute in tua pa manpah uh a, a singlamteh suanin Jesuh’ nung zui-in a puasak uh hi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Jesuh’ nung zui-in mi tampi tak pai uh a, tuate lakah Jesuh kahin a tamlawh numei pawlkhat zong a kihel hi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Jesuh zong amaute lamah kihei a, “Jerusalem khua numeite aw, kei hong kah kei unla, note le na tate uh a dingin kap un.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh mite in, ‘Ta a nei ngei lo, naungek nawi a teepsak ngei lo numei ciingte mi hampha mahmah ahi hi,’ a cih hun hong tung ding hi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Tua hun hong tun ciangin mite in, ‘Mual lian mual neute in hong cipnelhin a si khin hi lehang utzaw hang,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Singkung hing bang ahi kei tungah hih bangin hong bawl uh ahihleh singkung keu bang ahi note tungah hong nak hihzaw kan ding uh hi lo ahi hiam?” a ci hi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Mi that ahi, thonga kikhum mi nih zong, Jesuh tawh thahkhawm dingin a paipih uh hi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> “Lutang Guh,” a kicihna mun a tun uh ciangin singlamteh tungah Jesuh kilhcip uh a, tua mi that mi nihte zong, Jesuh’ taklamah khat, a veilamah khat kilhcip uh hi.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ahi zongin Jesuh in, “Pa aw, amaute in bang hih ihi hiam cih thei lo uh ahih manin a mawhna uh na maisak in,” a ci hi. Tua ciangin amau’ ngah ding ciat a theih nadingun ai sanin a puante a hawm uh hi.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Jew mi upate in Jesuh zahko-in, “Amah in midangte honkhia hi. Pasian teelsa Khrih ahih takpi leh amah le amah kihonkhia ta hen,” ci-in a simmawhbawl laitakun tua lai-a ding mite in a enen uh hi.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Galkapte in zong zahpihbawl uh a, a kiangah hong pai-in leenggahzu thuk pia uh a,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> “Jew Mite’ Kumpipa na hih takpi leh nang le nang kihonkhia in,” a ci uh hi.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> “Jew Mite’ Kumpipa hi,” ci-in a kigelh lai zong ama tung sanah kisuang hi.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Amah tawh a kikhai khawm mi that pa khat in zong Jesuh zahko a, “Nang Khrih hi lo na hi hiam? Nangmah kihonkhia inla, tua ciangin kote zong hong honkhia in,” a ci hi.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Ahi zongin a khat pa in a lawmpa taii a, “Pasian nangawn kihta lo na hi hiam? I vekpi-in gim hong kipiakna kibangkim hi.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ei tegel pen i gamtatna tawh kizui-in thu hong kikhen ahih manin ahi ding mah ahi hi. Ahi zongin amah in khialhna bangmah nei lo hi,” a cih khit ciangin",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Jesuh kiangah, “Jesuh aw, Kumpi-in nong pai ciangin kei zong hong phawk in,” a ci hi.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Jesuh in ama kiangah, “A mantakin ke’n kong cihin-ah: Tuni-in Paradais-ah kei tawh na omkhawm ding hi,” a ci hi.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Tua hun laitak pen sunkim nai sawm le nih pawl hi a, ni mial ahih manin nitak lam nai thum ciang dong leitung khempeuhah khua mial a,",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> tua hun sungin biakinn sung dalna puan kikekin phelnih a suak hi.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Tua ciangin nakpitakin Jesuh kiko a, “Pa aw, nangma khut sungah keimah kong ki-ap hi,” a cih khit ciangin a si ta hi.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Galkap mangpa in hih thupiang a muh ciangin Pasian phat a, “Hih pa, mihoih taktak khat ahi hi,” a ci hi.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Hih thute a en dingin a hong pai mihonpite in a thupiang teng a muh uh ciangin dahin dip humsa-in a ciah uh hi.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Galilee gam panin Jesuh a hong zui amah a thei ngei mite le numeite in gal et uh ahih manin a thupiang khempeuh a thei uh hi.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Tua laitakin Josef a kici mi khat om a, Judea gam sunga om Arimathea khuami ahi hi. Amah pen mihoih, a zahtakhuai mi khat hi a, Pasian’ Uk ding hun lamenin a ngakngak mi khat ahi hi. Amah pen ulian thuvaihawm sunga kihel hi a, ahi zongin a lawmte’ vaihawmna leh a nasepnate uh thukimpih lo hi.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Hih mipa Pilat kiangah va pai-in Jesuh’ luang a ngen hi.",
