			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Galilee gam panin a hong zui numeite in zong a kivuina-ah zui uh ahih manin a hanphual le a luang kisialzia khempeuh zong a mu uh hi.",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Tua ciangin amaute ciah uh a, Jesuh’ luang a nuh dingun paknamtui le sathau a bawlkhol uh hi. Thukham zui-in Sabbath ni tawlnga-in a om uh hi."
