			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Tua ciangin amau tegel sung panin Kleopas a kici pa in, “Jerusalem-a hawhte lakah tusawng tenga tua lai-a thupiang a thei lo nang bek na hi ding hi,” ci-in a dawng hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Tua ciangin Jesuh in amaute kiangah, “Bang thu ahi hiam?” ci-in a dot ciangin amaute in, “Nazareth khuami Jesuh tunga thupiang ahi hi. Amah pen kamsang khat hi a, Pasian le mite khempeuh in a thugen le a nasepna-ah vang a nei mahmah khatin a ngaihsut uh ahi hi.",
