			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Tua ciangin ka lawmte uh pawlkhat zong hanah va pai uh a, numeite’ gen bang teekteekin va mu uh a, ahi zongin Jesuh mu lo uh hi,” ci-in a dawng hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Tua ciangin Jesuh in amau tegel kiangah, “Bangzah takin hai a, bang dingin kamsangte’ thugen um thei lo na hi uh hiam?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Khrih in minthanna a ngah nadingin hih bangteng a thuak ding kisam hi lo ahi hiam?” a ci hi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Tua ciangin Jesuh in Lai Siangtho sungah ama thu a kigennate khempeuh, Moses laibu a kipanin kamsangte’ laibu khempeuh a khiatna a gen hi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Tua khua a tun uh ciangin Jesuh a paisuak ding bangin hong om a,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> ahi zongin amau tegel in kho-in, “Tu-in nitak lam hita a, ni tum dektak ahih manin ko tawh hong tamkhawm in,” a ci uh hi. Tua ahih manin Jesuh zong amaute tawh a tam hi.",
