			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Note pen hih thu khempeuh a thei teci na hi uh hi.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Ka Pa’ hong ciamsa thu, note tungah ka hong pia ding hi. Ahi zongin vantung panin tua vangliatna na ngah mateng uh hih Jerusalem khuapi-ah na ngak un,” a ci hi.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Tua ciangin Jerusalem khuasung panin Bethany khuagei ciang amaute paipih a, tua lai panin a khut laamto-in amaute thupha a pia hi.",
